quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  35,19,"“Ndipo wakhungu ndi wopenya ngosafanana, (woyenda pa njira ya choona ndi wosokera ngosafanana)"
  35,20,“Ngakhale mdima ndi kuunika (nzosafanana)
  35,21,“Ngakhale mthunzi ndi kutentha (nzosafanana)
  35,22,"“Ndipo amoyo ndi akufa safanana (amene mitima yawo ili ndi moyo pokhala ndi chikhulupiliro, ndi amene mitima yawo ili yakufa posakhala ndi chikhulupiliro, ngosafanana). Ndithu Allah akumumveretsa amene wam’funa; koma iwe sungathe kumumveretsa amene ali m’manda"
  35,23,"“Iwe sindiwe chinthu china, koma ndiwe mchenjezi"
  35,24,"“Ndithu Ife takutuma mwachoona kuti unene nkhani yabwino (yokalowa ku Munda wamtendere kwa amene akhulupirira), ndi kuti uchenjeze (za chilango cha Moto kwa amene sadakhulupirire). Ndipo palibe m’badwo uliwonse koma mchenjezi adapitamo"
  35,25,"“Ndipo ngati angakutsutse (sichachilendo), ndithu amene adali patsogolo pawo adatsutsanso. Aneneri awo adawadzera ndi zizindikiro zoonekera poyera, ndi malemba ndi buku lounikira (njira yabwino)"
  35,26,“Kenako ndidawalanga (ndidawaononga) amene adatsutsa. Nanga chidali bwanji chilango Changa (pa iwo)
  35,27,"“Kodi sudaone kuti Allah amatsitsa madzi kuchokera ku mitambo? Choncho kupyolera m’madziwo tatulutsa zipatso zautoto wosiyanasiyana (zakuda, zofiira, zachikasu, zobiriwira, pomwe madzi ake ndiamodzi omwewo). Ndipo m’mapiri muli timizere; toyera ndi tofiira tosiyana utoto wake, ndi (tina) takuda kwambiri"
  35,28,"“Ndipo mwa anthu ndi nyama zokwawa, ndi ziweto, nchimodzimodzinso; nzosiyana maonekedwe ake (utoto wake). Ndithu odziwa ndi amene amamuopa Allah mwa akapolo Ake. Ndithu Allah Ngwamphamvu zoposa; Ngokhululuka kwambiri"
  35,29,"“Ndithu amene akuwerenga buku la Allah uku nkumapemphera Swala moyenera napereka m’zimene tawapatsa mwanseri ndi moonetsera, iwo akuyembekezera malonda osaonongeka"
  35,30,“Kuti akawakwaniritsire malipiro awo ndi kuwaonjezera zabwino Zake; ndithu Iye Ngokhululuka kwabasi; Ngothokoza kwambiri